Dear Pritam Ghosh, 

 With reference to your application no. 397 for Internship at IISER Bhopal,
we are pleased to inform that you have been selected for internship entitled
“Dna Nanoelectronics” under the guidance of Dr. Kuntal Roy, Department
of Electrical Engineering And Computer Science.
 
 Kindly submit your acceptance by April 20th by filling out the Google form
by Clicking here. It will be assumed that you are not interested in the
internship if no response is received by the deadline, and the offer will be
automatically withdrawn. 
 No further requests will be entertained in this regard.
 
 
 Please note the following:

 The Internship will start on May 26, 2025 and end on July 21, 2025. 

No stipend will be paid to you for carrying out Internship at IISER Bhopal. 

You must bring your Institute/government issued identity card and two colour
passport size photographs. 

No academic evaluation of the candidate will be done by the Academic Office.


After successful completion of Internship and submission of a detailed
project report, a certificate will be issued by the Faculty-in-charge. 

 Hostel Accommodation will be provided strictly for the duration of the
Internship, i.e. maximum of 02 months, according to the Advertisement (from
May 26 to July 21, 2025) only. Hostel rooms will be allotted on a sharing
basis on the day of reporting at IISER Bhopal at the allotted Hostel office.


Hostel accommodation: Hostel allotment for (Non-IISER Interns): Boys in
Hostel-6 and Girls in Hostel-5. (Internal interns’ students will be
allotted in their respective hostels on a sharing basis).

ON campus mess will be allotted to all Interns.

Hostel Room rent shall be Rs. 1500/- per month. Charges will be levied in
multiple of 15 days.

Steps to pay hostel charges through SBI Collect SBI I-Collect
(https://onlinesbi.sbi => State Bank Collect => Educational Institutions =>
Madhya Pradesh => Indian Institute of Science Education and Research Bhopal
=> Temporary Hostel Accommodation Fees).

A copy of the e-receipt of payment has to be submitted to the Hostel
Caretaker (hostel office) on the day of reporting IISER Bhopal. In case of
cancellation of internship, hostel rent paid may be refunded after deduction
of 10% administrative charges on production of e-receipt of payment proof,
after approval of the competent authority. Refund of hostel rent paid will
not be allowed after joining the internship program in the institute.

Students shall bring their own light Bedding and lock &key and personal
toiletries.

No personal electrical appliances (Kettle, Iron, Induction Cooker) is
allowed under any circumstances with in the hostel.

Accommodation will be provided on sharing basis.

Mess facility shall be provided on payment basis. Mess fee payment shall be
made directly to Mess Contractor as per actuals.

Hostel accommodation is confirmed to all eligible interns on sharing basis.

All Interns students should adhere to the rules that govern the hostel.
Web-link to hostel rules 
All Interns Directly reported to the faculty/department concerned.

Accommodation will not be available for Online Internship.

For any query you can drop an email on internship@iiserb.ac.in.
 

Sincerely,
Dean, Academic Affairs


